Cases heard: 15CF152 & 15CF298, Defendant William Lee Gamble in court with attorney Jonas Bednarek. ADA Long appeared for the State of Wisconsin. Court went over the rights & elements. Defendant pled no contest to count 1 in 15CF152 and count 6 in 15CF298. Court found defendant guilty, entered judgment, sentence withheld, 2 years probation in each case, conditions in both cases: Complete AODA and comply with all treatment recommendations. Submit DNA sample. $518 costs, $443 costs. Additional condition in 15CF298, 30 days jail start Sept. 26, 2016 at 7 p.m. Huber granted under jail rules, may transfer to Dane County Jail. Court authorizes electronic monitoring but makes no ruling. Court granted 6 days jail credit on 15CF298, not applied to condition time.  No jail credit in 15CF152. All remaining counts dismissed.
